{"tid":470758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【當年今日】 1941年11月16日，加拿大部隊抵達香港參與「香港保衛戰」","createTime":"2017-11-16T15:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T15:46:47.000Z","uid":38671,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"649f3d0ad6463c7815df760cf0b7e227ac779ebc","tid":470758,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/s480x480/11214256_194040750930701_5925553229416921980_n.jpg?oh=65896c44e84105275b8c5d5184089872&amp;oe=5A97E3DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fs480x480%2F11214256_194040750930701_5925553229416921980_n.jpg%3Foh%3D65896c44e84105275b8c5d5184089872%26oe%3D5A97E3DA&h=177adb1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1941年11月16日，加軍抵港協防。<br />\n<br />\n近2,000人的加拿大部隊於1941年10月27日出發，經歷19日海上旅程終於抵港。加軍抵港後，駐港英軍被分成「大陸旅」和「港島旅」，前者於九龍及新界布防，後者則負責港島地區。<br />\n<br />\n「港島旅」由加拿大援軍司令羅遜（John K. Lawson）指揮，下轄米度息士營、溫尼柏榴彈兵營（The Winnipeg Grenadiers）、加拿大皇家來福槍營（The Royal Rifles of Canada）、香港防衛軍及曉士軍團。密德塞克斯營負責港島沿岸防守、溫尼柏營負責港島西南、來福槍營負責港島東南、香港防衛軍用作二線防衛、曉士軍團守備北角發電廠。"},{"pid":"4b4bfbe3f893cfc1bf150206032dc790223af927","tid":470758,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五毛唔會入呢個post啦掛，係咪好驚下個到你就無糧出</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、民國復興、群龍共舞、優美開始、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、JR、RedBaron (Epiphany)、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4c188d1674f4f3964fbebaf188b8645bb7b9380e","tid":470758,"ui